Interface EbXMLRegistryPackage

  • All Superinterfaces:
    EbXMLRegistryObject, EbXMLSlotList
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    EbXMLRegistryPackage21, EbXMLRegistryPackage30

    public interface EbXMLRegistryPackage
extends EbXMLRegistryObject
    Encapsulation of the ebXML classes for RegistryPackageType.

    This class contains convenience methods and provides a version independent abstraction of the ebXML data structure.

    Jens Riemschneider
